column1: Prompt
A serene river scene with boats drifting lazily along the water and birds nesting in the trees painted by Eugene Boudin.
A bustling market square with vendors selling fruits, vegetables, and seafood under colorful awnings depicted by Eugene Boudin.
A majestic seascape with storm clouds gathering on the horizon and waves crashing against the rocky shoreline painted by Eugene Boudin.
